==English==
===Etymology===
[[sentence]] + [[case]], from its meaning as the [[letter case]] [[pattern]] typically used in an English [[sentence]].

===Noun===
{{en-noun|-}}
# the manner in which [[capitalisation]] is used within a sentence.
# the standard capitalisation of an English sentence, with the first letter [[uppercase]] and subsequent letter [[lowercase]] with exceptions such as [[proper noun]]s or [[acronym]]s.

